name: Reel Deal Slots: Treasures of the Far East
name_original: Reel Deal Slots: Treasures of the Far East
description:
Reel Deal Slots: Treasures of the Far East is a game developed by Phantom EFX. It came out on 01-09-2009. It was published by Phantom EFX.
Reel Deal Slots: Treasures of the Far East is available on PC.
